<emphasis id="C880EAAFFFF7FFBFFD7150DAF1E7FF74" box="[725,994,163,189]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="82">Hipposideros galeritus</emphasis>
Cantor, 1846
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
